        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8619",
        "content": "The wave roamer bode riding at anchor, its owner awaiting. As they hastened onward, Hrothgar's gift they lauded at length.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
