        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8619",
        "content": "His hoard of bliss that old ill doer open found, who, blazing at twilight the barrows haunteth, naked foe dragon flying by night folded in fire: the folk of earth dread him sore.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
