        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8619",
        "content": "-- Now haste is best, that we go to gaze on our Geatish lord, and bear the bountiful breaker of rings to the funeral pyre.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
