        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8619",
        "content": "The dragon they cast, the worm, o'er the wall for the wave to take, and surges swallowed that shepherd of gems. Then the woven gold on a wain was laden -- countless quite!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
